Name: Canon EOS R5 Mirrorless Camera Body

This is ideal for dynamic action photos such as athletes, animals or vehicles in motion.rnUp to 20 fps Electronic (Silent) ShutterrnEspecially helpful for wildlife photography, journalism and situations where photographers need to remain discrete, the EOS R5 camera features a selectable electronic (silent) shutter mode, and can capture images at up to 20 fps. With a fast AF/AE system, DIGIC X image Processor and high-speed recording with new Dual CFexpress card slots, the EOS R5 helps ensure that camera operations are performed quickly and precisely.rnDual Pixel CMOS AF covering Approx. 100% Area with 1,053 AF AreasrnHigh-speed Focusing with Dual Pixel CMOS AFrnThe EOS R5 camera's highly responsive Dual Pixel CMOS AF system features an incredible 1,053 Automatic AF zones that can be designated as auto-focus focal points (when Face + Tracking priority AF is selected). This ensures higher-precision Eye Detection AF, or allows for you to focus on the desired AF point. Fast action can be captured and focus can be maintained with speed, accuracy and ease.rnAF Area Coverage of Approx. 100% x 100%rnThe EOS R5 camera features an expansive focus area of approx. 100% horizontal and 100% vertical when working with select RF and EF lenses. This means fast and impressive focusing even when composing your subject far from the center of the frame.rnEV -6 Low-light AutofocusrnAmazing for nighttime photography or in very low light settings, the EOS R5 camera's brilliant AF can operate in light as dim as a light rating of EV-6 where other AF systems may fa…

Description: Small Speakers, Big SoundThe size of 2 stacked Rubik’s Cubes®, Min 22 delivers beyond expectation. Min 22 adds a dedicated low frequency driver over the smaller Min 12. It’s designed to be teamed with a mix of Minx speakers, including one of our subwoofers for a full sound.Equally at home on the study, the dining room or as a key component in your home theatre set-up.BMR Speaker TechnologyUnlike traditional pistonic or flat panel speakers, Balanced Mode Radiator (BMR) drivers combine vertical and horizontal dispersion using horizontal vibration modes. Compared to conventional drivers, BMRs give pinpoint accuracy, offering extraordinary detail at low and high volumes. This means BMRs can deliver a much wider sound-stage, perfect when size and flexibility of placement matters.Spot-on SoundMinx Min 22 compact speakers offer 180° sound dispersion, so they’re easy to position and sound great wherever you are – as there’s no sweet-spot. You can place them vertically or horizontally on the optional table stand. The 4th generation BMR drivers deliver enhanced performance, so integrate beautifully with a Minx subwoofer to deliver a room-filling sound.Made to PleaseMinx Min 22 compact speakers are encased in high-gloss lacquered ABS cabinets, with the special BMR speaker drivers mounted to die-cast aluminium exoskeletons, they’re reassuringly solid. They’re designed to focus the sound and to propel your music out into the room.Choice of FinishUnderstated design ensures that no matter your interior decoration style, Minx Min 22 is always at home. Finished in high-gloss black or white, these compact speakers are beautifully subtle and unobtrusive. Choose black to hide them in the shadows and on bookshelves, or white to compliment a modern minimalist living room.Well ConnectedMinx Min 22 have proper speaker cable connectors (binding posts) and come with banana plugs for quick installation. A recessed screw fitting accepts the supplied flush wall bracket, or any of our dedicated accessories. The slender floorstands are ideal for surround systems, while the table stand allows Min 22 to be mounted horizontally – perfect for a centre dialogue speaker.Features SOUND THAT DEFIES ITS SIZEHuge sound from a little speaker and with wide frequency response and pin-point accuracy.WIDER SOUND DISPERSIONNo matter where you place them, or where you are in the room, Minx sounds great thanks to innovative Balanced Mode Radiator (BMR) drivers .ADDITIONAL DEDICATED DRIVERExtra speaker driver offers improved bass handling and wider frequency response.INCREDIBLE VERSATILITYOptional wall mount, floor stands, or desk stands offerComplete control of placement making for a better home audio or cinematic listening experience.SUBTLE DESIGN AND PREMIUM FINISHAvailable in gloss white.Specifications SENSITIVITY (SPL)88dB (2.83 Vrms input)FREQUENCY RESPONSE120Hz-20kHzIMPEDANCE8 Ohms compatibleRECOMMENDED AMP POWER25 - 200WDIMENSIONS (W X H X D)78 x 154 x 85mm (6.0 x 3.1 x 3.3”)WEIGHT0.75kg (1.65lbs)FINISHESHigh gloss whiteIN THE BOX1x speaker For more information, please visit the manufacturer's website.

Name: Thermoelectric Peltier Refrigeration Cooling System DIY Kit With TEC-12706 Peltier
Short description: Peltier modules are used for generating cooling effect using electricity. Simply connect to 12V 5A+ power supply and you will see frost appear on the aluminum p...
Description: Peltier modules are used for generating cooling effect using electricity. Simply connect to 12V 5A+ power supply and you will see frost appear on the aluminum plate within a minute. This assembly comes with the best Peltier we could get, so it can get even colder than the stand-alone module we sell, but we think the price is worth it. The 12V Peltier module is mounted onto a 12V heatsink and fan assembly with thermal paste and an aluminum clamp. Comes with the Peltier, heatsink, fan all assembled. You'll need a power supply to power it, we suggest our 12V 5A wall adapter. We show a temperature meter in a photo but that's not included, its just to show you how cold it gets. With the wide applications of semiconductor cooling, more and more DIY enthusiasts are interested in it. It's a question that how to make refrigerating capacity to a more great extent in water-cooling applications. This DIY kit could be just the answer that you are looking for. The DIY kit is a semiconductor cooling kit that uses a TEC1-12706 Thermoelectric Cooler 6A Peltier Module. The kit has 2 heat sinks: the bigger one is for the hotter side and the smaller one is for the cooler side. The bigger the heat sink, the greater dissipation of the heat. The fan, also included in this kit acts as a radiator. This is attached to the bigger heat sink. The TEC1-12706 thermoelectric Peltier module is sandwiched between the two heat sinks. The module will reduce the temperature. The kit when assembled takes up less space and is ideal for Pet Space air conditioning( dogs house, chicken, etc), small refrigerator, etc

Description: This heatsink might be useful for who needs a low noise solution with ODROID-XU4. The stock active cooler mounted on the XU4 is more efficient at dissipating heat away from the processor for most of use cases. But if you need a fan-less quiet system, this tall heatsink could be a solution. You can replace the active cooling fan with this passive heatsink. Down the max CPU clock of the XU4 to 1.4GHz if your system gets thermal throttling often. - Dimension : 40.0 x 40.0 x 25.0 mm (approx.) - Blue anodizing surface - Package includes a thermal paste tube. The thermal paste is responsible for conducting heat from the processor to the heat sink. Reassembling without applying thermal paste will cause the processor to overheat.

This accessory is particularly beneficial for those who wish to operate their Raspberry Pi 5 without a case, especially during periods of sustained heavy workloads.The Active Cooler is ingeniously designed, combining a large metal heatsink with a variable-speed blower to effectively dissipate the heat generated by the Raspberry Pi 5. This feature allows for customization of the cooling performance based on the temperature requirements of the Raspberry Pi 5. Description: intel Core i5-14600KF Desktop Processor 14 cores (6 P-cores + 8 E-cores) up to 5.3 GHzr The Intel Core i5-14600KF is a mid-range processor from Intel’s 14th generation lineup, known as "Raptor Lake." Here’s a more detailed look at its features and capabilities:r Specifications: tCores and Threads: 14 cores (6 Performance-cores (P-cores) + 8 Efficient-cores (E-cores)), with 20 threads. The P-cores handle demanding tasks and single-threaded workloads, while the E-cores handle background processes and multi-threaded tasks.r tBase Clock Speed: Typically lower than the boost clock speed, but it provides a baseline for performance.r tMax Turbo Frequency: Up to 5.3 GHz, which means it can reach high speeds under load for improved performance in tasks that benefit from higher clock speeds.r tCache: Usually features 20 MB of Intel Smart Cache (L3), which helps speed up access to frequently used data.r tTDP (Thermal Design Power): Typically around 125 watts, which helps in determining the cooling solutions needed. Features: tUnlocked for Overclocking: The "KF" designation means this processor is unlocked, allowing enthusiasts to overclock it for even higher performance, provided they have a compatible motherboard and adequate cooling.r tNo Integrated Graphics: The "F" in KF denotes the lack of integrated graphics, so you'll need a dedicated GPU for display output.r tSupport for DDR5 and DDR4: Compatible with both DDR5 and DDR4 memory, giving you flexibility depending on your budget and performance needs.r tPCIe 5.0 Support: Supports PCIe 5.0, offering faster data transfer speeds for compatible GPUs and storage devices. our facebook

DESCRIPTION REBELLIOUS AND DISTINCT The MAG CORELIQUID C Series liquid coolers' water block features a large surfaced ARGB lighting that is sure to dazzle your build. It is split into four pieces of unique diamond-cut areas, with three capable of lighting up and the last one featuring our proud MSI logo emblem. LGA 1700 COMPATIBLE The MAG CORELIQUID C Series liquid cooler provides out of box support for LGA 1700. RADIATOR PUMP DESIGN The pump has been integrated into the radiator for sound dampening and noise reduction. Additionally, placing the pump into the radiator also increases the pump's life expectancy by moving it away from the heat source. HIGH THERMAL DISSIPATION A split pathway through the radiator rapidly dissipates heat, cooled liquid is then pumped back into the loop. PUMP MOTOR RESONANCE ELIMINATION A durable three phase motor at the core of the pump generates minimal vibrations for long-lasting operation. EVAPORATION PROOF TUBING Constructed with three layers of netted plastic tubing and a reinforced mesh exterior. EXTENSIVE COMPATIBILITY Stylish yet built for flexibility, the MAG CORELIQUID C Series has been designed with a secure installation bundle with compatibility on a number of Intel and AMD motherboards.

Description: Price: $549.99(as of Sep 03,2020 06:15:02 UTC - Details)  The Apple MacBook Air "Core i5" 1.8 13" (Mid-2012/USB 3.0) features a 22-nm "Ivy Bridge" 1.8 GHz Intel "Core i5" processor (3427U) with two independent processor "cores" on a single chip, a 3 MB shared level 3 cache, 4 GB of onboard 1600 MHz DDR3L SDRAM (which cannot be upgraded after purchase), 128 GB flash storage, and an "integrated" Intel HD Graphics 4000 graphics processor that shares system memory. This all is packed in a razor thin (0.11-0.68 inch), 2.96 pound, aluminum case with an integrated 720p "FaceTime HD" webcam, a backlit full-size keyboard and a 13.3" widescreen TFT LED backlit active-matrix "glossy" display (1440x900 native resolution). Connectivity includes 802.11a/b/g/n Wi-Fi, Bluetooth 4.0, analog audio out, a "Thunderbolt" port, two USB 3.0 ports, and an SDXC-capable SD card slot. It lacks internal Ethernet, although an external Thunderbolt adapter was offered as a US$29 option. Compared to its predecessor, this model has a very similar external enclosure, although it has the aforementioned USB 3.0 ports and a new thinner and wider "MagSafe 2" power connector. Internally, however, it has a faster processor, architecture, graphics, RAM, and storage. Description: Price: $899.99 - $814.99(as of Jan 27, 2022 16:13:08 UTC - Details)  The MacBook Pro "Core i7" 2.6 15-Inch (Late 2016 Retina Display, Touch Bar, Four Thunderbolt 3 Ports) features a 14 nm, 6th Generation "Skylake" 2.6 GHz Intel "Core i7" processor (6700HQ), with four independent processor "cores" on a single silicon chip, a 6 MB shared level 3 cache, 16 GB of onboard 2133 MHz LPDDR3 SDRAM (which cannot be upgraded), 256 GB of PCIe-based flash storage, and dual graphics processors -- an AMD Radeon Pro 450 with 2 GB of dedicated GDDR5 memory and an integrated Intel HD Graphics 530 graphics processor that shares memory with the system. Description: Welcome to the latest iteration of the Odroid H-Series board, the Odroid H4+. This is the best all-rounder of the new generation Odroid H4 Series of boards. Specifications-wise, the Odroid H4+ has an Intel 4-Core N97 processor, accepts DDR5 SODIMM RAM (up to 48GB), and has options for Dual BIOS installations. It is equipped with four SATA ports, and a second Ethernet port, making it the best choice for users who need mass storage for high-performance NAS and/or use it for routing capabilities. Click Here For Full System Specification Sheet - Including Full Benchmark Data Top Line Feature Set Compared to the Odroid H3+:- Faster CPU architecture - Alder Lake N vs. Jasper Lake. Plus AVX2 extensions. Faster DRAM interface DDR5 4800 MT/s vs. DDR4 2933 MT/s. Higher base and boost CPU frequencies and more powerful iGPU. The increase from 2 to 4 SATA ports allows connection to a greater number of storage devices. An additional DisplayPort added allows the simultaneous use of up to 3 monitors. We also implemented little details following the ODROID-H3 feedback we received from all of our users. Examples of this are: Dual BIOS: If the BIOS is corrupted due to a power outage during update, etc., you can boot into the backup BIOS and recover by moving the jumper next to the DC jack. This feature is only available on ODROID-H4+ and ODROID H4-Ultra. BOARD DETAIL:- A. Description: Refurbished Lenovo ThinkCentre M920q TinyFor real results, you need real powerWith the latest generation of Intel processors, cutting-edge DDR4 memory, and the option of solid-state storage, the compact ThinkCentre M920 Tiny is as powerful and responsive as a full-sized desktop. It enables you to get more things done, more quickly and with more elbow room, too.What are you waiting for?For an even faster, smoother, and more responsive PC experience, opt for a hard drive with Intel Optane memory. By recognizing the way you work, this smart next-gen technology accelerates everything from booting up and opening large apps, to finding files fast and multitasking seamlessly.It's good to have high-speed connectionsWhen it comes to ports, the ThinkCentre M920 Tiny has plenty. It includes USB 3.1 Gen 2 technology for faster charging and data transfers, even if your PC is shut down or in sleep mode. The ports are placed conveniently too, enabling you to hook up an extra hard drive or monitor in seconds.Can fit and work anywhereOn a bookshelf, behind a monitor, under the desk you can fit your ThinkCentre M920 Tiny anywhere. Whats more, it's been rigorously tested to MIL-SPEC standards, so it works in almost any environment from the Arctic to the desert and everywhere in between.Easy to use, configure, & upgradeIf your PC is out of reach, you can switch it on remotely with a simple shortcut, Alt+P. The ThinkCentre M920 Tiny also has a number of expansion slots, enabling it to be configured to meet your business needs. Whats more, should you need to swap out any components, you can slide off the side panel without any tools.Go green, save greenWith Energy Star 7.0 and EPEAT Gold ratings, the ThinkCentre M920 Tiny is proven to be extremely energy efficient, resulting in cost savings in the long run. It also runs very quietly and proudly bears the world's first Ultra Low Noise Certificate, awarded by TUV Rheinland.One less thing to worry aboutEvery ThinkCentre M920 Tiny is equipped with Smart USB Protection. It lets you restrict what USB devices can access the PC, while ensuring that no malware enters the system or network through USB ports. In addition, there's TPM, or the Trusted Platform Module, providing hardware-based security, including the generating and storing of cryptographic keys, while a Kensington Lock port lets you physically secure your M920 Tiny.

Description: Descriptiont SeeedStudio A203 Mini PC w/ Jetson Xavier NX 8GB, 128GB SSD, 2xUSB 3, RS232, WiFi/BLE, Caset Compact yet powerful with 21 TOPs AI powert Equipped with a variety of I/Os for versatilityt Designed for a wide temperature range (-20 to 80 °C)t Features advanced embedded AI systemt Comes with pre-installed NVIDIA JetPack 5.0.2The A203 Mini PC w/ Jetson Xavier NX 8GB, 128GB SSD, 2xUSB 3, RS232, WiFi/BLE, Case is a compact, yet powerful, intelligent edge computer designed to bring cutting-edge AI capabilities to edge computing. Despite its smaller form factor compared to the Jetson NX Developer Kit, it delivers the same level of AI power, reaching up to 21 TOPs. The system is equipped with a variety of IOs, including HDMI, USBs, RS232, and CAN.This Mini PC is an excellent choice for applications in smart cities, security, industrial automation, and smart factories, among other edge AI solutions. It offers exceptional AI performance and ample storage, along with a comprehensive set of IOs, including HDMI, 2x USB3s, RS232, I2Cs, and GPIOs. It is designed to operate in a wide temperature range, from -20 to 80 °C, making it suitable for AI-embedded industrial and functional safety applications.The A203 Mini PC is characterized by its incredibly compact form factor, measuring just 100 x 44 x 59 mm. This edge AI box houses a Jetson Xavier NX 8 GB production module, a carrier board with rich interfaces, a 128 GB NVME SSD, a WIFI module, a heatsink, a fan, and an enclosure case.It features an advanced embedded AI system, including 384 NVIDIA CUDA® Cores, 48 Tensor Cores, 6 Carmel ARM CPUs, and two NVIDIA Deep Learning Accelerators (NVDLA) engines. The carrier board is equipped with a variety of I/Os, including 1 x RJ45 Gigabit Ethernet, 1x HDMI, 1x Audio Jack, 2x USB 3, 1x Micro USB, CAN, a microSD Card Slot, and a reset button. The system is also energy efficient, with the Jetson Xavier NX module delivering server-class performance.The A203 Mini PC comes with NVIDIA JetPack 5.0.2 pre-installed, making it an ideal platform for developing AI systems for smart factories, automated optical inspection, and other AIoT embedded systems. It supports alwaysAI Accelerated Edge Deployment, enabling the training of a new custom model in just a few hours. Alternatively, one can choose from over 130 pre-trained models from the always dashboard, deploy it to the A203 Mini PC, and build a computer vision application in minutes.The A203 Mini PC is particularly well-suited for intelligent video analytics and industrial automation applications. Leveraging the NVIDIA® TensorRT library and Deepstream framework, users can maximize the capabilities of the NVIDIA® Jetson™ processors. With all optimizations applied, it is possible to achieve desktop GPU-level framerates with deep learning algorithms in embedded form factors.View moreWhat's Includedt 1x A203 Mini PCt 2x Antennat 1x Power Adapter (without power cord)Dimensionst 100 x 50 x 59 mm (L x W x H)LinksPDF Filet A203 Mini PC w/ Jetson Xavier NX 8GB, 128GB SSD, 2xUSB 3, RS232, WiFi/BLE, Case - DatasheetSpecificationst Extremely small form factor full system: The edge AI box measures 100mm x 44mm x 59mm and includes the Jetson Xavier NX 8GB production module, a rich-interfaces carrier board, a 128 GB NVME SSD, a WIFI module, a heatsink, a fan, and an enclosure case.t Advanced embedded AI system: It features 384 NVIDIA CUDA® Cores, 48 Tensor Cores, 6 Carmel ARM CPUs, and two NVIDIA Deep Learning Accelerators (NVDLA) engines.t Built with rich sets of I/Os: The A203 carrier board includes 1x RJ45 Gigabit Ethernet, 1x HDMI, 1x Audio Jack, 2x USB 3, 1x Micro USB, CAN, microSD Card Slot, and a reset button.t Energy efficient: It operates with a +9V to +19V DC Input at 3A. The Jetson Xavier NX module delivers server-class performance, offering up to 14 TOPS at 10W or 21 TOPS at 15W or 20W.t Pre-installed NVIDIA JetPack 5.0.2: It supports the entire Jetson software stack and various developer tools for building fast and robust AI applications. It is provided by Seeed Edge AI partners and helps develop innovative AI solutions for manufacturing, logistics, retail, service, agriculture, smart city, healthcare, and life sciences, among others.

Name: SparkFun BlueSMiRF V2 Bluetooth Wireless Serial UART Link (3.3-5V)
Short description: Descriptiont SparkFun BlueSMiRF V2 Bluetooth Wireless Serial UART Link (3.3-5V)t Robust wireless Bluetooth linkt Seamless serial data transmissiont Compatible w...
Description: Descriptiont SparkFun BlueSMiRF V2 Bluetooth Wireless Serial UART Link (3.3-5V)t Robust wireless Bluetooth linkt Seamless serial data transmissiont Compatible with various baud ratest Supports OTA firmware updatest Built-in voltage regulator & logic level shiftingThe SparkFun BlueSMiRF V2 Bluetooth Wireless Serial UART Link (3.3-5V) serves as a robust wireless Bluetooth serial link, facilitating the replacement of serial cables with a wireless serial UART pipe. This device allows for seamless pairing, connection, and transmission of serial data across TX/RX lines, supporting a wide range of baud rates for serial streams. It boasts duplex transmission capabilities, ensuring accurate buffering, transmission, and delivery of data streams between two devices.The BlueSMiRF V2 comes with several enhancements over its predecessor, maintaining compatibility with the pinout of previous Bluetooth Mates and USB-to-serial converters. This compatibility ensures ease of integration with a variety of development boards and high-precision GNSS breakout boards. To connect to another device, users will need to solder a 1x6 female header or striped wires to the provided PTHs.For short-range applications, the BlueSMiRF V2 is ideal, offering reliable point-to-point communication within a 100ft (33m) indoor range. It can be paired with phones or computers for data viewing or remote control, and two BlueSMiRF units can be connected with the onboard PAIR button. The device also allows for remote configuration via a serial terminal app on a phone, with a simple AT command set to adjust settings such as baud rate and flow control. Additionally, it supports OTA updates for firmware enhancements.The BlueSMiRF V2 includes an onboard voltage regulator, logic level shifting circuitry on all pins, and two built-in LEDs to indicate connection status and serial UART traffic. It primarily supports Bluetooth classic (Serial Port Profile or SPP) and also offers BLE protocol support for a wider range of devices.Please note that the device requires an RS232 to TTL converter for higher voltages, and the voltage regulator can be bypassed with a jumper on the board. Bluetooth® classic (Serial Port Profile or SPP) is the primary supported protocol, compatible with Android phones, most desktops, and laptops, while BLE protocol support is available for all Apple phones.View moreWhat's Includedt 1x SparkFun BlueSMiRF V2 Bluetooth Wireless Serial UART Link (3.3-5V)Dimensionst 44.2 x 15.22 mm (L x W)LinksPDF Filet SparkFun BlueSMiRF V2 Bluetooth Wireless Serial UART Link (3.3-5V) - SchematicsMultimediaSpecificationst Espressif's ESP32-PICO-MINI-02 Module with Built-in PCB Antennat Serial Bluetooth Point-to-Point Communicationt Bluetooth Protocols Supported: Serial Port Profile (SPP), Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE)t Firmware Over-the-Air (OTA) Updates via 2.4GHz WiFit Recommended Input Voltage: 3.3V to 5Vt Current & Power Consumption at 3.3V: Idle: 72mA / 238mW, Connected with no Serial Traffic: 75mA / 248mW, Constant Duplex Serial Traffic: 140mA / 462mWt AP2112K 3.3V/600mA Voltage Regulatort Logic Level Converters on all pinst Standard Serial Port Broken Out to PTHs: RTS/RXI/TXO/VCC/CTS/GNDt PTHt Reset Buttont Pair Buttont LEDs: CONNECT, STATUSt Jumpers: 3.3V Bypass Jumper (JP2), Pair Button (BTN)

Description: Descriptiont Waveshare PoE UPS Mini-Computer for RPi CM4, GB Ethernet, 2 HDMI, 4 USB2.0 (US)t Versatile CM4 socket compatibilityt Integrated Gigabit Ethernet with PoEt Dual HDMI ports supporting 4K 30fpst M.2 M KEY slot for NVME SSDst Real-time clock with wake-up featureThe Waveshare PoE UPS Mini-Computer for RPi CM4, GB Ethernet, 2 HDMI, 4 USB2.0 (US) ports is an uninterruptible power supply and mini-computer designed specifically for the Raspberry Pi Compute Module 4. This versatile product features a CM4 socket compatible with all variants of the Compute Module 4, as well as parallel 18650 Li-ion battery support (batteries not included).The board is equipped with a Gigabit Ethernet RJ45 connector, which includes an integrated 802.3af-compliant PoE circuit (5V/2.5A). Additionally, it offers four USB 2.0 Type-A ports, a Raspberry Pi 40PIN GPIO header, and an M.2 M KEY slot for connecting NVME SSDs or communication modules with a PCIE M.2 M KEY interface.For display and camera connectivity, the base board provides one MIPI DSI port, two MIPI CSI-2 ports, and two HDMI ports with support for 4K 30fps output. It also includes a real-time clock with a battery socket, enabling the Compute Module 4 to be woken up when needed.For the Compute Module 4 Lite (without eMMC) variants, a MicroSD card socket is available. The board also features a fan with adjustable speed and measurement (5V/12V), M.2 status LED, CM4 status LED, and a power input range of 7-36V.View moreWhat's Includedt 1x CM4-POE-UPS-BASEt 1x Aluminum Alloy caset 1x Fant 1x Power Supply Adapter (US-Plug)t 1x ScrewdriverDimensionst 175 x 108 mm (L x W)LinksWebsitet Waveshare PoE UPS Mini-Computer for RPi CM4, GB Ethernet, 2 HDMI, 4 USB2.0 (US) - WikiSpecificationst Power Input: 7 - 36 Vt CM4 sockett Battery support: parallel 18650 Li-ion battery x 3 (Batteries not included)t Networking: Gigabit Ethernet RJ45 connector, integrates 802.3af-compliant PoE circuit (5V/2.5A)t USB: USB 2.0 Type A x4t Connector: Raspberry Pi 40PIN GPIO header, M.2 M KEY slott Display: MIPI DSI port x1 (22pin 0.5mm FPC connector)t Camera: MIPI CSI-2 port x2 (22pin 0.5mm FPC connector)t Video: HDMI x2, supports 4K 30fps outputt RTC: Real-time clock with a battery socket and the ability to wake Compute Module 4t Storage: MicroSD card socket for Compute Module 4 Lite (without eMMC) variantst Fan: allows speed adjustment and measurement, 5V/12Vt Indicator: M.2 status LED, CM4 status LEDt Weight: 742 g

Name: RC522 RFID 13.56MHz Read/Write Card Reader
Short description: Description The RFID Module RC522 Kit is a low-cost MFRC522 based RFID Reader Module that is easy to use and can be used in a wide range of applications. The MF...
Description: Description The RFID Module RC522 Kit is a low-cost MFRC522 based RFID Reader Module that is easy to use and can be used in a wide range of applications. The MFRC522 is a highly integrated reader/writer IC for contactless communication at 13.56 MHz. Features Highly integrated modulation and demodulation circuit; A small number of external devices can be used to connect the output driver stage to the antenna; Support ISO / IEC 14443 TypeA and MIFARE® communication protocol; The communication distance with ISO 14443A / MIFARE® in the reader mode is up to 50mm, depending on the length and tuning of the antenna. Supports ISO 14443 212kbit / s and 424kbit / s higher transmission rate communication. Support MIFARE® Classic encryption; 64-byte send and receive FIFO buffer; Flexible interrupt mode; Programmable timer. It has three power-saving modes: hardware power down, software power down, and transmitter power down. The first two modes are similar to MFRC500 and CL RC400. Its unique “transmitter power down” can turn off the internal antenna driver, that is, turn off the RF field Built-in temperature sensor to automatically stop RF transmission when the chip temperature is too high Adopt multiple independent sets of power supply to avoid mutual interference between modules and improve the stability of work With CRC and parity check functions, the 16-bit long CRC calculation polynomial of the CRC coprocessor is fixed as x16 + x12 + x5 + 1, which conforms to ISO / 1EC14443 and CCTITT protocols Internal oscillator, connected to 27.12MHz crystal Operating Current :13-26mA/DC 3.3V Idle Current :10-13mA/DC 3.3V Sleep Current:: less than 80uA Peak Current: less than 30mA Operating Frequency: 13.56MHz Environmental Operating Temperature: -20-80 degrees Celsius Environmental Storage Temperature: -40-85 degrees Celsius Relative humidity: relative humidity 5% -95% Data transfer rate: maximum 10Mbit/s (SPI) Module Dimension: 39 x 60 mm Package Include 1 x RC522 board 1 x 13.56MHz Key tag 1 x 13.56MHz Card 1 x 8 ways straight header pin 1 x 8 ways right angle header pin

Description: A truly versatile wide-angle zoom featuring an advanced optical design and constant f/4 maximum aperture, the Canon EF 11-24mm f/4L USM Lens is a member of the esteemed L-series of lenses designed for full-frame EOS DSLRs. One Super UD element and one UD element offer a significant reduction in chromatic aberrations while four aspherical elements help to minimize distortions throughout the zoom range and provide consistent edge-to-edge sharpness and illumination. Both SWC and ASC coatings have been applied to the elements in order to reduce lens flare and ghosting for increased contrast and color accuracy. Ideally suited for landscape and architectural photography, this lens covers ultra-wide to wide-angle perspectives and backs up its versatile zoom range with sophisticated optical components and intuitive handling.

Name: Sony Planar T* FE 50mm f/1.4 ZA Lens
Short description: The type of lens that will suit any photographer and almost any situation, is this New Sony 50mm f1.4 Zeiss. The 50mm focal length, which has become a proven st...
Description: The type of lens that will suit any photographer and almost any situation, is this New Sony 50mm f1.4 Zeiss. The 50mm focal length, which has become a proven standard throughout photographic history, in unison with the lightning-fast maximum aperture, make for a very versatile lens, with the ability to produce tack sharp images, time after time. Handheld shooting is a reality and not a dream with this ruggedly constructed prime lens, while an optical construction typical of this premium Sony Compact System Camera range, assures distortion and aberration-free images. Utilise the bright f1.4 aperture to create stunning bokeh in your portraits.

Name: Sony E 70-350mm f/4.5-6.3 G OSS Lens
Short description: The Sony 70-350mm f4.5-6.3 G OSS. is compatible with APS-C format models, and this lens provides an astonishing 105-525mm equivalent zoom range, while it manage...
Description: The Sony 70-350mm f4.5-6.3 G OSS. is compatible with APS-C format models, and this lens provides an astonishing 105-525mm equivalent zoom range, while it manages to keep your kit as possible, weighing in at only 625 grams. It features a fast and near-silent XD Linear AF motor and Optical SteadyShot. This lens is primed for a life of action.

Name: Olympus M. Zuiko Digital ED 75-300mm f/4-8-6-7 II Lens
Short description: The Olympus M. Zuiko Digital ED 75-300mm f/4-8-6-7 II Lens is the ideal telephoto zoom lens for Olympus OM-D & Pen cameras. Whether your interests are wildlife ...
Description: The Olympus M. Zuiko Digital ED 75-300mm f/4-8-6-7 II Lens is the ideal telephoto zoom lens for Olympus OM-D & Pen cameras. Whether your interests are wildlife photography or sports and action, this will be your go to lens. Olympus have managed to produce another superb, high performance lens in their compact system range.

Name: SONY E 10-18MM F4 OSS LENS
Short description: Take on ultra-wide landscapes or tight interiors with your APS-C-format E-mount camera by using the SONY E 10-18MM F4 OSS LENS. Delivering a super wide 15-27mm ...
Description: Take on ultra-wide landscapes or tight interiors with your APS-C-format E-mount camera by using the SONY E 10-18MM F4 OSS LENS. Delivering a super wide 15-27mm equivalent zoom range, and offering a constant f/4 aperture, this lens can produce high-quality images in a variety of difficult scenarios. The implementation of one Super ED and three aspherical elements further guarantees image quality by minimizing aberrations throughout the range. Also, the lens is equipped with Optical SteadyShot image stabilization for reducing the effects of camera shake. Beyond these features, the lens also features an internal focus design that enables fast, responsive autofocus and a minimum focus distance of 9.8". Additionally, it has a seven-blade circular diaphragm for smooth bokeh. Designed for APS-C-format E-mount cameras, this ultra-wide-angle 10-18mm lens will provide a 15-27mm equivalent zoom range. A constant f/4 maximum aperture offers consistent performance throughout the zoom range and also lends greater control over focus position for shallow depth of field techniques. One Super ED (extra-low dispersion) glass element is featured in the lens design to help reduce chromatic aberrations and color fringing for improved clarity and color neutrality. Three aspherical elements are incorporated in the lens design to reduce astigmatism, field curvature, coma, and other monochromatic aberrations. Optical SteadyShot image stabilization helps to minimize the appearance of camera shake for sharper imagery when shooting handheld with slower shutter speeds. This stabilization system can also be combined with select camera's sensor-shift type image stabilization for more effective control of camera blur. An internal focus mechanism contributes to faster, more responsive autofocus, the minimum focus distance of 9.8", and easier handling as the lens does not change in length during use. Rounded seven-blade diaphragm contributes to a pleasing bokeh quality when employing selective focus techniques.

Name: Sigma 8-16mm F/4.5-5.6 DC HSM Ultra-Wide Zoom Lens for Canon
Short description: The Sigma 8-16mm F/4.5-5.6 DC HSM is an ultra-wide zoom that has a 35mm equivalent angle of view of a 12-24mm lens when used on DSLRs with APS-C size image sens...
Description: The Sigma 8-16mm F/4.5-5.6 DC HSM is an ultra-wide zoom that has a 35mm equivalent angle of view of a 12-24mm lens when used on DSLRs with APS-C size image sensors. Sigma's FLD glass elements, equal to fluorite glass, correct for distortions and color aberrations to deliver beautiful high contrast images.

Name: Sony FE 16-35mm f/2.8 GM Lens
Short description: With its superb f2.8 constant maximum aperture, this Sony FE 16-35mm f/2.8 GM Lens should be your go-to lens for handheld and low-light performance. Designed fo...
Description: With its superb f2.8 constant maximum aperture, this Sony FE 16-35mm f/2.8 GM Lens should be your go-to lens for handheld and low-light performance. Designed for full-frame E-Mount cameras, the versatile zoom range finds the wide angle lens usable for landscapes, architectural shots and interiors, as well as travel snaps and everyday documentation. Sony's excellent Direct Drive Super Sonic Wave AF motor will please both still and video enthusiasts, with its fast, quiet and exceptionally accurate performance, while an easy to access focus hold button can be used for pinpointing a selected area of focus.

Name: Sony FE 85mm f1.4 GM lens
Short description: A short telephoto focal length and bright f1.4 aperture make this Sony FE 85mm f1.4 DM lens perfect for portraiture. Designed for use on the full frame E-Mount ...
Description: A short telephoto focal length and bright f1.4 aperture make this Sony FE 85mm f1.4 DM lens perfect for portraiture. Designed for use on the full frame E-Mount cameras, this lens has been designed for premium performance, with extra-low dispersion and extreme aspherical elements in the mix for reducing aberrations and increasing image sharpness and clarity. Combining with the large maximum aperture is an eleven-blade circular diaphragm for stunning out-of-focus, blurred areas, while a dust and moisture resistant construction enable consistent performance in more trying conditions

Name: Panasonic Lumix DC-S1R with 24-105mm Lens Kit

Description: One of a pair of Panasonic’s new releases into the full-frame mirrorless world, is this high-resolution Lumix S1R. Using the existing Leica SL-Mount, and announced alongside a range of high-quality lenses, you won’t find trouble creating a versatile new kit, and taking advantage of the full-frame 47MP sensor. While its sibling, the S1, is notable for being a multimedia friendly model, this S1R is best for capturing the most exceptional detail imaginable, with its previously mentioned sensor without a low-pass filter, and a high-performance Venus engine processor on its side.

Description: Measuring just 1-3/16" (30.2mm) when fully retracted, the Sony 16-50mm retractable zoom lens is super compact and easy to carry so you can quickly whip out your camera and spontaneously grab shots as they occur. It's perfect for traveling and other scenarios that require a lightweight, compact camera and lens combo. It covers a 16mm to 50mm range (35mm equivalent = 24-75mm) for flexible shooting, and is equipped with one ED (extra-low dispersion) and four aspherical elements, resulting in a high-performance lens that is surprisingly compact.

Name: Canon PowerShot SX620 HS Digital Camera
Short description: The Canon Powershot SX620 HS proves ideal for everyday photography and travel, due to its versatility and user-friendly nature. On the imaging front the SX620 e...
Description: The Canon Powershot SX620 HS proves ideal for everyday photography and travel, due to its versatility and user-friendly nature. On the imaging front the SX620 excels, thanks to the HS system provided by the sensor and DIGIC 4+ processor. This system proves brilliant in low-light conditions, where images are noiseless and high in clarity, while its high-speed nature results in the camera being able to shoot Full HD video at 30 fps and stills at 7.1 fps. The lens on the front of this Compact Digital Camera is where it really shines, with a 25x optical zoom range - great for wide-angle landscapes, tightly-cropped portraits, sports and more.

Name: Canon EOS M6 Mk II Mirrorless Camera Body
Short description: The Canon EOS M6 Mk II is a stylish mirrorless camera with a high-resolution APS-C-sized 32.5MP CMOS sensor, Dual Pixel autofocus and captures 4K/30p video from...
Description: The Canon EOS M6 Mk II is a stylish mirrorless camera with a high-resolution APS-C-sized 32.5MP CMOS sensor, Dual Pixel autofocus and captures 4K/30p video from the full width of its sensor. The Dual Pixel CMOS AF provides 5481 selectable points for smooth, fast focusing for both photo & video and offers continuous stills shooting up to 14 fps with AF and AE tracking. Weighing only 408g, the EOS M6 II is a super-compact, well built camera with a comfortable ergonomoc grip, 3-inch tilting 180˚ touchscreen, and built-in Wi-Fi/Bluetooth® connectivity for easy image sharing.

Name: Canon PowerShot SX70 HS
Short description: Bolstering the power and reach of a full high-end kit, but maintaining a compact stature, the Canon Powershot SX70HS is your ticket to well-rounded, easy shooti...
Description: Bolstering the power and reach of a full high-end kit, but maintaining a compact stature, the Canon Powershot SX70HS is your ticket to well-rounded, easy shooting. The 65X optical zoom lens covers an equivalent range of 21-1365mm, which is suitable for limitless applications, including landscapes, sports and beyond. The 10 frames per second continuous shooting is perfect for tackling subjects on the go, while 4K UHD video recording helps you frame those situations where a still picture will not suffice. With built-in IS, you are unleashed to explore the full length of the zoom range, even in lower light situations, without camera shake spoiling proceedings, while built-in WiFi and Bluetooth opens the doors for premium levels of remote control and image sharing.

Description: The Canon EF-M Lens Adapter offers the flexibility to shoot with the entire EF and EF-S range of lenses when using the EOS M body. AF is possible when using the Mount Adapter. Whether it s macro, wide-angle, standard, telephoto or super telephoto lenses, your creativity is limitless with the new mount adapter.

Name: Panasonic Lumix DC-S1H Body
Short description: The New full-frame Mirrorless Panasonic Lumix S1H is the ideal body for those with a serious interest in videography. 6K24p video resolution is possible with th...
Description: The New full-frame Mirrorless Panasonic Lumix S1H is the ideal body for those with a serious interest in videography. 6K24p video resolution is possible with the S1H, using all of the camera's large sensor, while 4K60p resolution is possible with interrnal 4:2:2 10-bit sampling. Still photography has not been ignored in this release, with the 24.2MP Full-Frame sensor producing crisp and sharp images, and other high-end features lending a helping hand, including 9 frames per second continuous shooting and 5-axis in-body Image Stabilisation. To frame photos and videos, make use of the large 3.2-inch touch LCD-screen, or the high-resolution OLED EVF. As well as the previously mention stabilisation, the Panasonic Lumix S1H features a photo and video friendly speedy AF system, showcasing Panasonic's Depth from Defocus technology, with 225 contrast detection areas.

Name: Nikon Z6 Body with FTZ Mount Adapter
Short description: The Nikon Z6 Mirrorless Camera with FTZ mount adaptor is positioned as the "all-arounder" within the new Z System. Beginning with the Z Mount itself, a large-di...
Description: The Nikon Z6 Mirrorless Camera with FTZ mount adaptor is positioned as the "all-arounder" within the new Z System. Beginning with the Z Mount itself, a large-diameter design with a short 16mm flange distance allows Nikon to create compact, yet powerful cameras and develop more advanced optics. The Z6 is among the first in the series, and features a high-performing FX-format 24.5MP BSI CMOS sensor and the EXPEED 6 Image Processing Engine delivering outstanding image quality and speed with a native sensitivity range of ISO 100-51200.

Thanks to the L series build quality and weather sealing, you can use this versatile lens in most weather conditions.

Short description: Brand: BeatsColor: Moon GrayFeatures: Custom acoustic platform delivers powerful, balanced sound Control your sound with two distinct listening modes: Active No...
Description: Brand: BeatsColor: Moon GrayFeatures: Custom acoustic platform delivers powerful, balanced sound Control your sound with two distinct listening modes: Active Noise Cancelling (ANC) and Transparency mode Three soft eartip sizes for a stable and comfortable fit while ensuring an optimal acoustic seal Up to 8 hours of listening time (up to 24 hours combined with pocket-sized charging case) Industry-leading Class 1 Bluetooth for extended range and fewer dropouts High-quality call performance and voice assistant interaction via built-in microphones IPX4-rated sweat and water resistant wireless earbuds Beats wireless headphones and earphones are compatible with Apple and Android devices What’s in the Box – Beats Studio Buds True Wireless Noise Cancelling Earphones, charging case, eartips with three size options, USB-C to USB-C charging cable, Quick Start Guide, Warranty card (USB-C power adapter sold separately) Binding: ElectronicsRelease Date: 13-04-2022model number: MMT93LL/APart Number: MMT93LL/ADetails: DRIVEN BY PREMIUM SOUND Beats was born to deliver music as the artist intended. Beats Studio Buds are engineered to deliver powerful, balanced sound in a compact design, through an entirely customized acoustic platform. A proprietary, dual-element diaphragm driver resides within a two-chamber housing, resulting in clear sound with outstanding stereo separation. An advanced digital processor then optimizes audio performance for loudness and clarity, while simultaneously ensuring clean noise-cancellation. The result — immersive sound that pulls the emotion of music from the studio to your ears to keep you going all day long. CONTROL THE NOISE With two distinct listening modes, you are in total control of your sound. Active Noise Cancelling (ANC) continuously blocks unwanted outside noise using a finely-tuned filter that dynamically adapts to your surroundings. When you need to hear the world around you, switch to Transparency mode at the press of a button. The external-facing microphones mix the sounds of your surroundings back in with your music for a natural, ‘open’ listening experience. POWER YOUR DAY The earbuds have up to 8 hours of listening time1 with two additional charges provided by its pocket-sized charging case.2 That means that Beats Studio Buds give you up to 24 hours of combined playback. With ANC or Transparency mode turned on, you’ll get up to 5 hours of listening time, 15 combined with the case. If you need a little extra juice, 5-minute Fast Fuel charging gives up to 1 hour of playback3 when battery is low. Now that’s wireless freedom. CHOOSE YOUR FIT Three soft, silicone eartip sizes (small, medium, or large) give you a customized fit and create an acoustic seal for an even more immersive listening experience. These size options provide comfort, stability, and the confidence of staying put. Beats Studio Buds were made to fit seamlessly into your life with its sleek, compact in-ear design. Its matching charging case offers superior portability with a rounded, slim design that easily fits in your pocket or purse. Even better, the earbuds themselves offer an IPX4 rating for sweat and water resistance.4 KEEP THE CONNECTION With Class 1 Bluetooth® technology, Beats Studio Buds offer extended wireless range and fewer dropouts. Dual-beam forming microphones target your voice and filter out wind and external noise for high-quality call performance and elevated voice clarity. On-ear controls allow you to manage calls and control music. You’ll also be able to customize the “Press and Hold” function to work for either ANC or your voice assistant.5 COMPATIBLE WITH APPLE AND ANDROID Beats Studio Buds feature simple one-touch pairing for Apple6 and Android devices7 and easily connect via Bluetooth. With the Beats app for Android, you’ll get features like built-in controls, device status (i.e. battery levels), and firmware updates. With Apple devices, those features are built in to iOS with no app required, and and you can also activate Siri hands-free just by saying “Hey Siri”.8 And the USB-C charge connector provides a single charging solution across both Apple and Android platforms. 1 Testing conducted by Apple in April 2021 using preproduction Beats Studio Buds and Charging Case units and software paired with iPhone 11 Pro Max units and prerelease software. The playlist consisted of 358 unique audio tracks purchased from the iTunes Store (256-Kbps AAC encoding). Volume was set to 50% and Active Noise Cancellation and Transparency were turned off. Testing consisted of full Beats Studio Buds battery discharge while playing audio until the first Beats Studio Buds stopped playback. With Active Noise Cancellation turned on, listening time was up to 5 hours. Battery life depends on device settings, environment, usage, and many other factors. 2 Testing conducted by Apple in April 2021 using preproduction Beats Studio Buds and Charging Case and software paired with iPhone 11 Pro Max units and prerelease software. Description: Price: $223.75 - $137.18(as of Sep 15, 2024 10:04:17 UTC - Details)  The 7750 eye 4 2GB GDDR5 PCI Express Graphics Card is a high-performance Short Form Factor (SFF) single slot card with four mini DisplayPort interfaces for digital signage applications. Only a company with over two decades of cutting edge development in graphics cards can bring you the power to drive up to four displays in independent, clone, or extended mode via a single PC. The VisionTek 7750 eye 4 2GB GDDR5 PCI Express Graphics Card is the hassle-free, high-performance digital signage solution for retail, hospitality, commercial, healthcare, and more. VersatileWhether you want to power a convenience store display, a multi-monitor display wall in a public venue, feed four individual monitors to separate rooms in your business office environment, the 7750 eye 4 is ready to present your desired message or content from a single PC. No Additional Power Supply NeededThanks to an energy efficient design, the 7750 eye 4 requires only 70 watts of power so it can be run off the system power bus. With most systems featuring a factory-installed 350 watt or higher power supply, you don't have to purchase and install a larger power supply. High Speed Memory for High PerformanceWhile consumer grade cards use common DDR3 memory, the 7750 eye 4 uses 2GB of higher bandwidth GDDR5 memory to deliver lag-free content with the highest resolution possible. Secure Cable ConnectionsThe 7750 eye 4 features a unique bracket that utilizes the included mini DP to DVI screw attaching cables and mini DP to DP adapters to prevent accidental cable disconnection. Small Form Factor - Low Profile DesignShort Form Factor (SFF) design fits in today's Low Profile desktops and workstations via the short bracket mounted on card. The card is convertible to standard ATX design with the included tall bracket for standard chassis as well. Four Independent Surround Sound Audio ChannelsBy incorporating Discrete Digital Multi-Point Audio technology into its chipset, the 7750 eye 4 is able to deliver HD 7.1 surround sound independently to four displays via the four interfaces on the card. Gone is the need for multiple PCs and cards to provide audio to multiple displays. And, you don't need a 3.5mm mini-DIN cable to connect to the motherboard. This attention to detail to support business application use via the mini Displayport interface is unmatched by any other graphics card manufacturer. Description: For sale is a fully tested and functional Xbox 360 Console Bundle: Minecraft, used, in good condition. Included in the package is the console, Minecraft (as a download), 1 controller, power adapter and video cable. Upgrade to include your choice of games, additional controllers or a larger hard drive capacity!r Xbox 360 Console Bundle: Minecraftr Minecraft focuses on allowing the player to explore, interact with, and modify a dynamically-generated map made of one-cubic-meter-sized blocks. In addition to blocks, the environment features plants, mobs, and items. Some activities in the game include mining for ore, fighting hostile mobs, and crafting new blocks and tools by gathering various resources found in the game. The game's open-ended model allows players to create structures, creations, and artwork on various multiplayer servers or their single-player maps.r XBOX 360 – FEATURESr Microsoft more than brought out the big guns with the Xbox 360, bringing a true powerhouse to the table. Not only did the system have some of the best specifications for its generation, but its user-friendly graphical interface makes using the system highly enjoyable.r STRONG SYSTEM ARCHITECTUREr In terms of specification, the Xbox 360 is an absolute beast, packing a triple-core Xenon CPU clocked at 3.2 GHz. Combined with its 500Mhz ATI graphics processor, it’s no wonder that it was the first console to truly bring HD gaming to the table, being capable of outputting on 1080p resolution straight out of the box.r ONLINE PLAYr Highly acclaimed at launch, Xbox Live revolutionized online multiplayer for consoles. Featuring voice chat, the Marketplace and Xbox Live Arcade, the high-speed, well-optimized feature really rose the bar for how we expect to play.r ACHIEVEMENTSr One of the Xbox 360’s most outstanding features are achievements – virtual awards for doing different tasks in each game. Each of them holds a certain number of points, which will keep you chasing them to get more gamer points than your friends!r XBOX 360 – THE GAMESr With over 2000 games released, the Xbox 360 library features a large number of outstanding titles, from Microsoft exclusives such as Halo, Fable and Gears of War to highly acclaimed Triple-A titles such as the Call of Duty series and even beautifully crafted indie games. Add backwards compatibility with the Original Xbox and you’re guaranteed to spend countless hours on titles you enjoy.r GRAND THEFT AUTO 5r Sitting at number 2 in the list of the best-selling video games ever, GTA 5 brings back the nostalgia of the series in a new setting, with much improved graphics and features. Set within the fictional state of San Andreas, based on Southern California, the single-player story follows three protagonists—retired bank robber Michael De Santa, street gangster Franklin Clinton, and drug dealer and arms smuggler Trevor Philips—and their efforts to commit heists while under pressure from a corrupt government agency and powerful crime figures.r HALO 4r Halo 4's story follows a cybernetically enhanced human supersoldier, Master Chief, and his artificial intelligence construct Cortana, as they encounter unknown threats while exploring an ancient civilization's planet. The player assumes the role of Master Chief who battles against a new faction that splintered off from remnants of the Covenant, a former military alliance of alien races, and against mechanical warriors of the Forerunner empire known as the Prometheans.r CALL OF DUTY BLACK OPSr Set in the 1960s during the Cold War, the game's campaign follows CIA operative Alex Mason as he attempts to recall certain memories in combat in order to locate a numbers station. This station is due to transmit broadcasts to sleeper agents who are bound to use chemical weapons across the United States. Locations featured in the game include Cuba, Laos, Vietnam, the Soviet Union, the United States, Hong Kong, and the Arctic Circle. The multiplayer of Black Ops features multiple objective-based game modes that are playable on 14 different maps included with the game.r GUITAR HERO 2r Like in the original Guitar Hero, the player uses a peripheral in the shape of a solid-body electric guitar to simulate playing rock music as notes scroll towards the player. Most of the gameplay from the original game remains intact, and provides new modes and note combinations. The game features more than 40 popular licensed songs, many of them cover versions recorded for the game, spanning five decades , from the 1960s to the 2000s.r SKYRIMr The game's main story revolves around the player's character, the Dragonborn, on their quest to defeat Alduin the World-Eater, a dragon who is prophesied to destroy the world. The game is set 200 years after the events of Oblivion and takes place in Skyrim, the northernmost province of Tamriel. Over the course of the game, the player completes quests and develops the character by improving skills. The game continues the open-world tradition of its predecessors by allowing the player to travel anywhere in the game world at any time, and to ignore or postpone the main storyline indefinitely.r XBOX 360 – FUN FACTSr r tThe system is named “360” because Microsoft didn’t want a lower number than on the upcoming PlayStation 3.r tDevelopment names for the system included Nextbox, Xbox Next, Xenon, and Xbox 2.r tXbox 360 models included the Xbox 360 Core, Xbox 360 Arcade, Xbox 360 Premium, Xbox 360 Elite, Xbox 360 Slim, and Xbox 360 E.

Please note: Photos are for reference only. Original Xbox for Sale hurry up and get discount.r Original Old Xbox Console - Featuresr A much-awaited console, the Xbox, was developed by Microsoft. In addition, it had many features that placed it above its competitors, remaining a beloved system for years to come!r Powerful Processorr The Xbox was graphically powerful compared to its rivals. It has a 733 MHz Intel Pentium III processor, a processor that could be found on a standard PC, and a built-in hard disk, a first in the console market.r Unique Storage Methodr Besides the 8 /10 GB internal hard drive capacity, the console has an 8 MB removable solid-state memory card. It can be plugged into the controllers, onto which game saves can be copied from the hard drive in the Xbox dashboard's memory manager or saved during a game.r Pc-like Characteristicsr Not only is the processor of the Xbox similar to one on a standard PC, but it also has a custom operating system that is based on a heavily modified version of Windows 2000. Furthermore, it could render DVD/CD at a high quality and also connect to the internet for online gaming through Xbox Live.r Original Xbox Console - Gamesr There are over 1000 games you can play on the original Xbox Console, many of which later became a staple in the gaming community and have come to be loved by many.r Halo 2r The best-selling Xbox Original game with over 8 million copies sold. In Halo 2, the player assumes the roles of both the human Master Chief and the alien Arbiter in a 26th-century conflict between the human United Nations Space Command, the genocidal Covenant, and the parasitic Flood. It features a new game engine, added weapons and vehicles, and new multiplayer maps.r Counter-Striker Almost everybody has heard of this multiplayer first-person shooter in which teams of terrorists battle to perpetrate an act of terror (bombing, hostage-taking, assassination). At the same time, counter-terrorists try to prevent it (bomb defuse, hostage rescue).r Fabler Fable takes place in the fictional nation of Albion. Players assume the role of an orphaned boy who realizes his dream of becoming a Hero. The choices players make in the game affect the perception and reaction to their Hero by the characters of Albion and change the Hero's appearance to mirror what Good or Evil deeds the Hero has performed.r Tom Clancy’s Splinter Cellr Follow the activities of NSA black ops agent Sam Fisher in this stealth-oriented game. Move through the shadows for concealment whenever possible as the game displays a "light meter" that reflects how visible the player character is to enemies. With the help of vision goggles and limited weapon ammo, discover secrets and reach your goals as a skilled agent.r GTA San Andreasr The game focuses on the story of former gangster Carl "CJ" Johnson. He is brought back home by the death of his mother. He went on to become involved in a long journey that saw him explore the fictional U.S. state of San Andreas.r Star Wars Knights Of The Old Republicr Taking place 4,000 years before the Galactic Empire, Knights of the Old Republic is a fantastic sci-fi RPG game. You take the role of a Jedi tasked with defeating Darth Malak, a Dark Lord of the Sith who has released a Sith armada against the republic. Lastly, the game's sound, story, dialogue, and battle systems have been highly acclaimed, earning it a spot on the best video games of all-time list!r Original XBOX - Fun Factsr r tBefore launching, anticipation for the Xbox was high. Toys 'R' Us and Amazon reported that online preorders sold out within 30 minutes.r tA special event was held before the launch at the Toys 'R' Us store in Times Square. 1,000 systems were shipped to the store to kick off sales.r tBill Gates was present at the event, personally selling the first system. He also played games with them at the numerous display units.

Upgrade to include games, an additional controller, or a memory card. Please note: Photos are for reference only.r Playstation 1 (PS1) – Featuresr PS1 is one of the most successful systems of all time. It not only marked Sony’s entry into the video game industry but also broke the sales record of the time, with over 100 million units sold.r Powerful Processorr With a clock speed of 33.86MHz and a graphics chip integrated into its processor, the Playstation 1 brought gaming to a new level. In addition, 2D and 3D games run fast and smoothly with high video quality.r Vastly Larger Gamesr With games coming on CD, both video and sound quality increased dramatically. The high space on the discs also pushed for far more complex games than what was available on the competing systems.r Playstation 1 – The Gamesr There are over 3000 games available for the PS1; the console has the most expansive library of its generation. In addition, you’re guaranteed to find something you’ll love in this vast collection of first-party, third-party and even homebrew games.r Crash Bandicoot 2r In the second game of the series, Crash is taken captive by the evil Doctor Neo Cortex. The crash is thrust into several parts of N. Sanity Island to gather Crystals that will allow Cortex to contain the power of an upcoming planetary alignment and keep the planet from being destroyed. In addition, the gameplay is similar to the first game, with Crash tasked with collecting the level crystal in 25 stages. Your abilities include jumping on enemies, sliding, spinning tornadoes, and performing body slams to deter enemies. Lastly, apart from the 25 levels, there are Bonus Paths spread across the game, where you can gain additional health and power-ups and finding them all is guaranteed to be a fun challenge.r Gran Turismor The best-selling PS1 title, Gran Turismo, was the most complex racing game of its time. It features an astonishing 140 cars and 11 race tracks, Arcade and Simulation modes. In the Arcade mode, you can choose your car and track, unlocking more as you win races. On the other hand, in Simulation mode, you will be earning different driver’s licenses to unlock new events, earn credits and win your way through its tournaments.r Tomb Raiderr This action-adventure title has you play as Lara Croft, an archaeologist hired to find an artifact called the Scion of Atlantis. On your quest, you will be tasked with clearing complex areas, solving puzzles and battling enemies. Lastly, the game received high appraisal for its detailed graphics, captivating story and engaging gameplay and went on to spawn one of the most acclaimed series in video game history.r Metal Gear Solidr A pioneer of the stealth genre, Metal Gear Solid has you play as Solid Snake. You are a special force operative tasked with neutralizing a nuclear threat posed by FOXHOUND, a renegade particular terrorist unit. You will navigate a nuclear facility trying to avoid being detected by guards. However, you can do this through various means, including crawling, ducking, taking cover and deploying the famous box method. Lastly, you can unlock a special survival mission if you finish the game. It will task you with finishing ten stages under a seven-minute time limit for additional fun.r Spyro The Dragonr In this acclaimed platformer, you will be playing Spyro, a dragon on a quest to save the five Homeworlds from the evil Gnasty Gnorc. Lastly, the game is easy to play and features fun, family-friendly graphics, making it an excellent fit for gamers of all ages!r Final Fantasy VIIr This highly acclaimed JRPG follows Cloud Strife. He is a mercenary who joins an eco-terrorist organization to stop a world-controlling megacorporation from using the planet's life essence as an energy source. Lastly, the game is a staple of the series and is the first Final Fantasy title to use full motion video and 3D computer graphics, superimposing 3D character models over 2D pre-rendered backgrounds.r Sony Playstation 1 (PS1) – Fun Factsr r tThe PlayStation was initially planned as a CD add-on to the Super Nintendo. But after a falling out with Nintendo, Sony decided to make their system.r t102 million consoles were sold before the PS1 was discontinued in 2004.r tThe console even outperforms high-end CD players costing thousands of dollars.r tThe original PS1 discs have a black base. But there was no particular value or feature to the black base of the disc. Learn more about the Playstation 1 here.

Included in the package is the console, 1 premium controller, a power cable, and a video cable. Upgrade to add your choice of games or a 2nd controller! Please note: Photos are for reference only. click herer Hyperkin MegaRetron HD - Featuresr The MegaRetron HD takes you back to the 90s, allowing you to play all your favorite SEGA Genesis titles without the trouble of finding a vintage system. The console is brand new, easy to set up and use, and bound to keep you enjoying your retro games for a long time. Relive that fast-paced 16-bit action that keeps you on the edge of your seat. The console even features that sleek, black & grey design that you’ve grown to know and love.r RETRO GAMING ON MODERN HARDWAREr The MegaRetron HD not only allows you to replay your favourite titles from the Genesis, but it also features HD upscaling, outputting video in crisp 720p. Pair this with a modern TV and your games will look better than ever! It also features a button which enables you to switch between 4:3 and 16:9 aspect ratios and comes with an AV cable so you can easily hook it up to your older TV sets. While the Genesis was impressive, the MegaRetron is even more powerful, ensuring you won’t face any video lag, regardless of how fast the game gets!r COMPATIBLE WITH GENESIS AND MEGADRIVE GAMESr The system’s lack of region locking makes it possible for you to play games from all around the world, released for both the Genesis and Sega Mega Drive. Now you can finally experience all the iconic titles from the console’s lifespan, be it a US, European or Japan-only game!r GENESIS CONTROLLER SUPPORTr While it comes with a premium controller made to replicate the original, it is also fully compatible with all SEGA controllers and peripherals, allowing you to play all your favourite titles just like you did back in the day!r SEGA GENESIS – THE GAMESr The MegaRetron is compatible with the Sega Genesis’ gigantic library of over 900 game, all of them having that iconic look and feel! You can go for classics like Sonic, NBA Jam, Mortal Kombat, or go explore more indie releases. Here are some of the classic games we suggest getting with your console:r SONIC THE HEDGEHOGr The game features an anthropomorphic hedgehog named Sonic in a quest to defeat Dr. Robotnik, a scientist who has imprisoned animals in robots and stolen the powerful Chaos Emeralds. The gameplay involves collecting rings as a form of health, and a simple control scheme, with jumping and attacking controlled by a single button.r SONIC THE HEDGEHOG 2r It is the second main entry in the Sonic the Hedgehog series, and introduced Sonic's sidekick, Miles "Tails" Prower, controllable by a second player. In the story, Sonic and Tails must stop series antagonist Dr. Ivo Robotnik from stealing the Chaos Emeralds to power his space station, the Death Egg.r MORTAL KOMBAT 2r The game's plot continues from the first game, featuring the next Mortal Kombat tournament set in the otherdimensional realm of Outworld, with the Outworld and Earthrealm representatives fighting each other on their way to challenge the evil emperor Shao Kahn. Also, Mortal Kombat 2 introduced more varied finishing moves (including several Fatalities per character) and new finishers.r NBA JAMr This video game based on the National Basketball Association found popularity with its photorealistic digitized graphics, over-the-top presentation and exaggerated style of two-on-two basketball play. NBA Jam allowed players to jump many times above their own height, make slam dunks that defy human capabilities, and freely shove or elbow opponents out of the way and get flagged. It also featured a variety of secret characters, as well as the ability to track player records and statistics between play sessions.r DISNEY’S ALADDINr Disney's Aladdin is a 2D side-scrolling video game in which the player controls Aladdin and his monkey Abu through several stages taking place throughout the city of Agrabah. You can also play as a fearsome Velociraptor, chasing Grant down and trying to prevent him from reaching the Visitor’s Center for added fun!r Sega Genesis- Fun Factsr r tIt is backwards compatible with its predecessor, Master System.r tThe console’s internal hardware was a mashup of an Apple Macintosh and a Game Boy.r tEven though official development of the console has stopped, enthusiasts still make games for the system.r tIn order to spark the interest of a younger audience, the design of the Sega Genesis was based on the appearance of audio-players and cars.r tThe console actually had 2 names. While in the rest of the world it was known as Mega Drive, in the USA it was renamed Genesis as a symbolic title representing a new era of Sega in the American marketplace.r tCreated as a mascot for Sega, Sonic the Hedgehog greatly increased the popularity of the Genesis in North America, and is credited with helping Sega gain 65% of the market share against Nintendo.

Description: Up for sale is a brand new, professionally assembled SCART RGB cable. It will automatically switch your TV into the highest possible quality signal from your system - RGB with sound sent to both speaker channels. It also includes 220uf capacitors and resistors to prevent your image from displaying too brightly. Please read because people keep buying the wrong cable! These cables were originally designed for CDX and then a second one was designed going the other direction for the Genesis 3 so “looking at the console” means that while you are plugging this in you are looking at the av socket on the side of the console - therefore: A cable going right travels in a direction going right of the AV socket. A cable going left travels in a direction going left of the AV socket. A cable going left when plugged into a Genesis 3 will travel to the back of the console, ergo is most suitable for that console. A cable going right when plugged into a CDX will travel to the back of the console, ergo is most suitable for that console. A cable going left is most suitable for Genesis 2. One that goes right will collide with the power in cable. Please see the pictures if unsure, as the pictures show the cable looking from the TOP side, as in the orientation they will be plugged in. This cable is fully compatible with the following Sega systems. Sega Megadrive 2 (UK or Japanese) Sega Megadrive 2 European (PAL or SECAM) Sega Genesis 2 32X Multimega CDX This cable is NOT compatible with the Genesis/Megadrive 1 or Master System 1 OR 2, so be careful!
